responsibilities:
1.Manage and oversee specific fresh category (fruits, vegetables, meat, seafood，dairy), developing category strategies and procurement plans;
2.Analyze market trends, consumer demand, and competition to optimize product assortment and improve sales and profitability;
3.Handle supply chain management, establish strong relationships with suppliers, conduct procurement negotiations, control costs, and optimize supply channels;
4.Monitor inventory and product turnover, develop promotional strategies to enhance inventory turnover and reduce waste;
5.Collaborate with various departments (e.g., procurement, logistics, marketing) to ensure smooth product supply, quality, and market promotion;
6.Stay updated on industry trends, policies, and regulations to ensure business compliance and continuously optimize procurement and operational processes;
7.Lead and train the team to enhance professional capabilities and work efficiency.

